sp. nov. 
<emphasis id="DCC3FBD0279E4D2C60C927E04DB61B14" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="79">A</emphasis>
thorax, dorsal view, male 
<emphasis id="D5572A1117D3886423C86EB52FD084F3" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="79">B</emphasis>
metaleg, lateral view, male 
<emphasis id="E9026CCFFBC102C5C0C452591F43841E" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="79">C</emphasis>
metaleg, lateral view, female. Scale bar: 2 mm.
</paragraph>
